---
// src/pages/privacy.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy: Data & Cookie Disclosures | petfoodcal" 
  description="Read the privacy policy of petfoodcal. Learn how we handle your data, our cookie usage, and our integration with Google Analytics."
  canonicalUrl="https://petfoodcal.vercel.app/privacy"
>
  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="bg-canvas-soft border-b border-hairline" style="padding: 80px 24px 64px;">
    <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-wider text-body inline-block" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Data Protection</span>
      <h1 class="display-lg font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Privacy policy</h1>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 15px;">
        Effective date: June 3, 2026. Learn how we respect and safeguard your privacy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="bg-canvas" style="padding: 64px 24px 80px;">
    <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto leading-relaxed text-body" style="font-size: 15px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px;">
      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">1. Protect Your Personal Data (Zero Collection)</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          At <strong class="text-ink">petfoodcal</strong>, we believe in complete privacy. We do not require account creation, logins, email addresses, names, or contact information to use our pet food calculator.
        </p>
        <p>
          Any parameters you input into the calculator (such as your pet's name, weight, age, and activity level) are processed entirely inside your local browser. They are not sent to our servers and are never sold or shared with any third party.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">2. Understand Local Storage Usage</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          To provide a seamless experience, our calculator uses your browser's local storage to remember your pet's inputs (like name, weight, and diet preferences). This is done so you do not have to re-enter this information when you reload the page.
        </p>
        <p>
          This data remains strictly on your device. You can clear this information at any time by clearing your browser cache or site data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">3. Monitor Traffic via Google Analytics and Cookies</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          We use Google Analytics, a web analysis service provided by Google LLC, to monitor aggregate website traffic trends (such as page views, user location trends, and bounce rates). Google Analytics uses cookies (small text files saved on your computer) to analyze how users navigate the site.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          The information collected is anonymized (including your IP address) and transmitted to Google servers. We use this aggregate data solely to improve the user interface and performance of the calculator.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can opt-out of Google Analytics cookies by installing the Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on or by using your browser's cookie settings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">4. View Third-Party Advertising Policies</h2>
        <p>
          We may display ads using services like Google AdSense. Ad networks may use cookies and web beacons to collect non-personal data (such as browser type, time of visit, and ads clicked) to serve targeted advertisements based on your interests.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">5. Contact Our Team with Questions</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us by emailing <strong class="text-ink">nadarnitesh32@gmail.com</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
